& [FrontierApplicationPlanDesign] is the design contract for applying a frontier advancement record to active conversation surfaces
  @ [conversation_kernel] src/negotiated_agent/conversation.py
  @ [frontier_advancement_record_design] coordination/frontier_advancement_record_design.sop
  @ [frontier_advancement_writer] src/negotiated_agent/frontier_advancement_cli.py
  @ [manager_job_notice] coordination/manager_job_notice.sop
  @ [created_at] 2026-05-30T02:24:00Z

  + [design_status] is ready_for_implementation_slice
  + [authority_boundary] is frontier_application_plan_not_manager_decision
  + [primary_goal] is define the explicit surface mutation plan required before applying a reviewed frontier advancement record
  + [non_goal] is creating Manager approval
  + [non_goal] is creating Shaliach clearance
  + [non_goal] is applying code to the target workspace
  + [non_goal] is silently editing project narrative without a recorded proof ref

& [PlanInputs] is what a frontier application plan must inspect
  + [required_ref] is frontier_advancement_record.sop
  + [required_ref] is active_conversation.sop pointer
  + [required_ref] is active conversation surface file
  + [required_ref] is project_narrative_surface.sop when narrative update is required
  + [authority_boundary] is application_plan_not_surface_write
  = must: verify active conversation current_frontier equals record previous_frontier
  = must: verify record authority_boundary is frontier_advancement_record_not_surface_mutation
  = must: verify next_frontier is non-empty and distinct from previous_frontier
  = must: preserve proof_refs and packet_refs as last_proof additions or linked refs

& [FrontierApplicationPlan] is the future dry-run artifact form
  + [field] is plan_id
  + [field] is advancement_ref
  + [field] is conversation_surface_ref
  + [field] is previous_frontier
  + [field] is next_frontier
  + [field] is proof_refs_to_append
  + [field] is completed_slice_refs_to_append
  + [field] is narrative_update_required
  + [field] is authority_boundary
  + [authority_boundary] is frontier_application_plan_not_surface_write
  = must: be writeable without mutating the conversation surface

& [FrontierApplicationResult] is the future mutation result artifact
  + [field] is result_id
  + [field] is plan_ref
  + [field] is applied_status
  + [field] is conversation_surface_ref
  + [field] is previous_frontier
  + [field] is next_frontier
  + [field] is appended_proof_refs
  + [field] is narrative_update_ref
  + [field] is authority_boundary
  + [authority_boundary] is frontier_application_result_not_code_apply
  = must: only be written after exact previous_frontier match
  = must: record skipped or blocked state rather than forcing stale application

& [ProofExpectations] is the minimum implementation proof for this design
  + [test_case] is valid advancement record produces application plan without mutating surface
  + [test_case] is stale active conversation frontier rejects plan creation
  + [test_case] is plan serializes proof refs and packet refs
  + [test_case] is result application updates current_frontier only with explicit apply command
  + [test_case] is stale apply writes blocked result and preserves surface

& [ImplementationOrder] is the safe next split
  + [slice_1] is add FrontierApplicationPlan record and dry-run planner helper
  + [slice_2] is add explicit CLI to write frontier_application_plan.sop
  + [slice_3] is add explicit apply command that mutates only the active conversation surface after exact frontier match
